        boolean handleUnknownAttribute​(Object instance,
                               QName attributeName,
                               IXmlParsingContext parsingContext)
        Callback used to handle an attribute that is unknown to the model being parsed.
        Parameters:
        instance - the Java instance that data is to be deserialized to
        attributeName - the name of the unknown attribute
        parsingContext - the context used for parsing
        Returns:
        true if the attribute was processed by this handler, or false otherwise
